<p style="float:left"><a name=research></a><b>Research Interests: </b></p>
<p style="float: right; padding-right:0.2in;">
[<a href="#top">Top</a>]
</p>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<p style="margin-top:0px">
I am interested in applying theory to systems. In particular, my research aims to leverage mathematical tools such as {Performance Modeling, Queueing Theory, Machine Learning, Control Theory} to analyze the behavior of systems such as {Distributed Systems, Cloud, Data Centers, ML Systems} and to optimize metrics of interest such as {Performance, Energy}.<br><br>
<!--
I am currently working with IBM Research on applying queueing theory and control theory to provide performance guarantees for cloud-deployed applications (via scale-out and scale-up in OpenStack).<br><br>
-->
